📚 Library Management System in Salesforce Cloud
(Mini Project – Complete Step-by-Step Guide)
🟢 STEP 1: Login to Salesforce
Open Salesforce
Login with your account
Click ⚙️ Setup
🟢 STEP 2: Create Custom Objects

We will create 3 objects:

Book
Member
Book Issue
📘 2.1 Create BOOK Object

Go to:

Setup → Object Manager → Create → Custom Object

Fill:

Field	Value
Label	Book
Object Name	Book
Record Name	Book Name

✔ Enable Reports
✔ Save

👤 2.2 Create MEMBER Object

Create another object:

Field	Value
Label	Member
Object Name	Member
Record Name	Member Name

✔ Enable Reports
✔ Save

📄 2.3 Create BOOK ISSUE Object

Create third object:

Field	Value
Label	Book Issue
Object Name	Book_Issue
Record Name	Issue Name

✔ Enable Reports
✔ Save

🟢 STEP 3: Create Fields in BOOK Object

Go to:

Book → Fields & Relationships → New

Add fields:

Field Name	Type
Book Title	Text
Author	Text
Category	Picklist
Available Copies	Number
📌 Category Picklist Values
Science
Fiction
History
Technology
🟢 STEP 4: Create Fields in MEMBER Object

Go to:

Member → Fields & Relationships → New

Add:

Field Name	Type
Member ID	Text
Department	Text/Picklist
Email	Email
Phone	Phone
🟢 STEP 5: Create Fields in BOOK ISSUE Object

Go to:

Book Issue → Fields & Relationships → New

Add:

Field Name	Type
Issue Date	Date
Due Date	Date
Return Date	Date
Status	Picklist
📌 Status Picklist Values
Issued
Returned
🟢 STEP 6: Create Relationships (VERY IMPORTANT)

In Book Issue Object create:

🔗 Relationship 1
Setting	Value
Field Type	Master-Detail Relationship
Related Object	Book

✔ Save

🔗 Relationship 2
Setting	Value
Field Type	Master-Detail Relationship
Related Object	Member

✔ Save

🟢 STEP 7: Add Fine Calculation
📌 Create Fine Formula Field

Go to:

Book Issue → Fields & Relationships → New

Choose:

Formula
Fill Details
Field	Value
Label	Fine Calculation
Return Type	Currency
Paste Formula
IF(
   Return_Date__c > Due_Date__c,
   (Return_Date__c - Due_Date__c) * 10,
   0
)
Meaning
₹10 fine per late day
If returned late → fine calculated automatically
Otherwise → 0

✔ Save

